    "Then, we type a goal, \"find some high-risk events in this city\".",
    "The dataset is introduced briefly, and the system proposes four initial exploration tasks based on our goal: sentiment analysis, keyword analysis, tags analysis, and spatial analysis (Fig. 4-a1).",
    "As the four tasks are aligned with our objectives, we bookmark them all in our progress.",
    "We then prioritize the exploration of the first task -sentiment analysis.",
    "Upon submission, the agent generates a time varying card at the Visualization view (Fig. 4-B)."
